name: Nifty Royale X Jonathan Winbush Sewer Shark

metadata.description: Sewer Shark is paying homage to one of my favorite videos on the Sega CD gaming system back in the 90s. The base version is a 1920 x 1920 60fps space ride through a futuristic corridor in space. The 1/1 winner will get a 2160 x 2160 60fps special edition of the NFT which enhances the visuals and has several elements in the ship react to the original audio which is also enhanced from the original.
metadata.name: Sewer Shark

attributes.value: Jonathan Winbush is a multi-award-winning motion graphics artist that has work with Epic Games, Marvel, Netflix, Warner Bros, DC, & Happy Madison to name a few.
